race.comment: JOKERS GRIN (1) was very impressive when winning the Prince Of Wales first-up, rounding up his rivals with ease as the odds-on pop. He'll get back from the wide barrier again today, but he may just be too classy for his rivals. Clearly WA's best sprinter at the moment and can continue his winning ways. ACROMANTULA (3) comes back to WA following a good stint in Victoria. His recent trial was impressive and the booking of CJP is a good push for his chances. Can sit on the speed from the inside barrier and can return with a bang. OSCAR'S FORTUNE (4) was very good in his first-up performance as he returned to the Luciani stable. The inside draw should see him on the speed once again for Pike and with improvement expected, he can be in the finish once again. SPACEWALK (2) makes his WA debut today for the leading stable and his trial coming in was solid. Won't be far away. REPOSSESSION (6) was sound in the Prince Of Wales and has to be included.
